Authorization:
Privilege:
  8 bits to represent access rights. 1 for enabled, 0 for disabled. Privilegs not mentioned are assumed to be implicitly enabled.
  Starting from LSB to MSB, each bit denotes
    1st: get personal campaigns
    2nd: get personal teams
    3rd: get all campaigns
    4th: get all teams
    5th: set personal campaigns' cost
    6th: set personal campaigns' ads
    7th: set personal teams
    7th: set all campaigns
    8th: set all teams
  i.e. Manager: 00111111, means a manager can do everything except setting all campaigns and teams (as some are owned by other managers)
  i.e. Creative Staff: 000100011, means he can get his own campaigns/teams, and update the ads for those campaigns
